  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Target concentration infusion(TCI) of remifentanil (2.0ng/ml) suppresses the cough induced by
      endotracheal tube more effectively than intravenous administration of lidocaine (1.5mg/kg).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
